	module.exports = {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Life is a YOLO game","author":"Henry Wu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"/home/circleci/project/src/pages/replace-security-groups-in-terraform.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-9f6e6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Terraform\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-526de.png 885w,\n/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/replace-security-group-with-terraform-ff8ce91af5afd8c6ea9b89ea5c410769-9f6e6.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2>AWS 的限制</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Security group 的 description 不可以更改，如果一定要更改，<strong>要先刪除之後再重建</strong>。</li>\n<li>EC2 跟 RDS <strong>至少要有一個</strong> security group，<strong>不可以完全沒有</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Terraform 的折衷辦法</h2>\n<p>以下每個步驟之間，都要輸入以下兩個指令，<strong>最後一步結束之後也要輸入</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ terraform plan\n$ terraform apply</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>不建議兩步合併一步做，因為可能會破壞掉 Terraform 的 <code class=\"language-text\">terraform.tfstate</code>。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>先在 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案裡，使用 <a href=\"https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/aws/r/security_group.html\">aws_security_group</a> 建立一個沒有 <code class=\"language-text\">ingress</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">egress</code> rule 的 dummy security group，然後新增到要抽換的 <a href=\"https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/aws/r/instance.html\">aws_instance</a> 或 <a href=\"https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/aws/r/db_instance.html\">aws_db_instance</a> 的 <a href=\"https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/aws/r/instance.html#vpc_security_group_ids\">vpc_security_group_ids</a> 裡。</li>\n<li>修改 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案的 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_instance</code> 或 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_db_instance</code> block，把要抽換掉的 security group 從 <code class=\"language-text\">vpc_security_group_ids</code> 移除掉。<strong>注意如果有公開的 port，instance 會全部斷網，如果有承諾 zero downtime 要想辦法避開</strong>，例如先把原來 security group 的 rule 全部複製到 dummy security group，可能會需要 <a href=\"https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/aws/r/security_group_rule.html\">aws_security_group_rule</a> 的協助。</li>\n<li>修改 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案，先移除或註解掉要抽換的 security group。<strong>注意一定要確定 security group 都從 instance 上 detach 了，否則 Terraform 在 apply 階段就會一直卡著</strong>。我個人推測是因為 AWS 的 API 也沒有直接針對 instance 至少要有一個 security group 這件事拋出錯誤，所以 Terraform 就會一直等待 AWS 回覆。</li>\n<li>修改 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案，把已經抽換掉的新 security group 重新 attach 回 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_instance</code> 或 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_db_instance</code> 的 <code class=\"language-text\">vpc_security_group_ids</code> 裡。</li>\n<li>修改 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案，將 dummy security group 從 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_instance</code> 或 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_db_instance</code> 的 <code class=\"language-text\">vpc_security_group_ids</code> detach 掉。</li>\n<li>修改 <code class=\"language-text\">*.tf</code> 檔案，移除或註解掉 dummy security group 的 <code class=\"language-text\">aws_security_group</code> resource block。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>結語</h2>\n<p>使用 Terraform 抽換 security group 的步驟不難但非常繁雜，很難想到有什麼原因會讓 AWS 不准使用者修改 security group 的 description。</p>","excerpt":"AWS 的限制 Security group 的 description 不可以更改，如果一定要更改， 要先刪除之後再重建 。 EC2 跟 RDS  至少要有一個  security group， 不可以完全沒有 。 Terraform…","frontmatter":{"title":"在 Terraform 抽換 Security Group","date":"March 06, 2017"}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/replace-security-groups-in-terraform/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/terraform-note/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Terraform 雜記"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/migrate-from-cloudflare-to-aws/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"從 Cloudflare 搬家到 AWS，而且是「徹底搬家」"}}}}

